The paper deals with image quality assessment and enhancement using machine learning, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of big data for training the regression module suggests that the paper may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. The paper also involves image processing techniques, which could place it under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
